take a nice rest.

08:12.559 --> 08:14.628
I think you're all
wasting valuable time.

08:14.661 --> 08:16.764
-Thank you.
-What you need to do

08:16.797 --> 08:18.365
is get a kidnapping sack.

08:18.398 --> 08:19.767
No, you need to get your go-bag.

08:19.800 --> 08:21.468
And you need to trust the plan.

08:21.501 --> 08:23.604
-Get your go-bag.
-Trust the plan.

08:23.637 --> 08:26.173
-Get your go-bag.
-Trust...

08:26.206 --> 08:28.475
Hey, you two may want
to have your argument

08:28.508 --> 08:30.511
